Package: didwrappers
Title: Expand functionality of the R 'did' package
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Ransi", "Clark", , "t.ransi.weerasooriya@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0003-5574-3450"))
Description: The package calculates differences-in-differences estimates at the unit-level instead of the group-level. It allows for an expanded suite of aggregation methods, including on custom time-invariant variables.
